    $(document).ready(function () {
            
        
        function getQueryStringValue(key) {
            return unescape(window.location.search.replace(new RegExp("^(?:.*[&\\?]" + escape(key).replace(/[\.\+\*]/g, "\\$&") + "(?:\\=([^&]*))?)?.*$", "i"), "$1"));
        }
               

        function searchSubmit() {                        
            //window.location.href = window.location.pathname + "?" + $.param({ 'search': $("#tbSearch").val() });
            if ($("#tbSearch").val() != "") {
                window.location.href = "/?" + $.param({ 'search': $("#tbSearch").val() });
            }

            if ($("#tbSearchMobile").val() != "") {
                window.location.href = "/?" + $.param({ 'search': $("#tbSearchMobile").val() });
            }
        }

        $("#tbSearch").autocomplete({
            source: availableTags,
            select: function (event, ui) {
                
                $("#tbSearch").val(ui.item.value);
                
                searchSubmit();
            }
        });

        $("#tbSearch").keydown(function (event) {
            
            var keypressed = event.keyCode || event.which;
            if (keypressed == 13) {
                searchSubmit();
                return false;
            }
            
        });


        $("#tbSearchMobile").autocomplete({
            source: availableTags,
            select: function (event, ui) {

                $("#tbSearchMobile").val(ui.item.value);

                searchSubmit();
            }
        });

        $("#tbSearchMobile").keydown(function (event) {

            var keypressed = event.keyCode || event.which;
            if (keypressed == 13) {
                searchSubmit();
                return false;
            }

        });


    });

        var width = $(window).width(), height = $(window).height();

            window.location.href = window.location.origin;

        function lnkClick(i) {
            $('.feature').hide();
            $('.pagination li a').removeClass('current');
            $('.pagination li a[data-index=' + i + ']').addClass('current');

            $('.next').removeClass("collapse");
            $('.prev').removeClass("collapse");

            $('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_hdnCurrentPage').val(i);

            if (parseInt($('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_hdnCurrentPage').val()) >= parseInt($('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_hdnPageCount').val())) {               
                $('.next').addClass("collapse");
            }
            if (parseInt($('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_hdnCurrentPage').val()) <= 1) {
                $('.prev').addClass("collapse");
            }
            $('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_txtInitLoad').val("0");
            $('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_btnPaging').click();            
        }

        function lnkPrev() {

            var prev = parseInt($('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_hdnCurrentPage').val()) - 1;

            if (prev > 0) lnkClick(prev);
            else lnkClick(0);
        }

        function lnkNext() {
            var next = parseInt($('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_hdnCurrentPage').val()) + 1;
            lnkClick(next);
        }

        function lnkFinal() {
            
            var final = parseInt($('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_hdnMaxPage').val());
            lnkClick(final);
        }

        switch ('featured') {
        case "latest":
            $('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_lnkLatest').addClass("active");
            break;
        case "popular":
            $('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_lnkPopular').addClass("active");
            break;
        case "featured":
            $('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_lnkFeatured').addClass("active");
            break;
        case "relavant":
            $('#MainContent_ctl00_ctl04_lnkRelavancy').addClass("active");
            break;
        }

        articleLoadAndResizeFunctions();

    </script>
